Reclusa::

She smiled and gave what would be seen as a slight curtsy toward
Hydras. "I am thankful for your hospitality. Yes please. I would
greatly like a tour and then shown my quarters. If I wish to perform
at optimum levels, I shall need a few hours recharge on the power
cells."  In a regal gesture, "By your leave." And then turned to
Perceptor, "Show me my new home. I want to know as much as I can so I
can defend it properly."
